Class Snowdata

java.lang.Object
  database.Snowflake
      database.Snowdata

public class Snowdata
extends Snowflake

Table snowdata manager. Each row in snowdata contain a position and and set of data measured at that position. The number of row is thus equal to the number of positions.

Author:
Jim Gunnarsson, di98jgu
